{"tid":1689122,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[IT手足入］發夢義載call車apps","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T16:41:31.000Z","uid":67103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1f34c87efe94a3f04f46acc14d339cf01f81014f","tid":1689122,"uid":67103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:40:25.000Z","msg":"其實之前有無人諗過整call義載apps（唔收錢既uber）呢樣野？？可以好似uber咁要影大頭驗證司機（防止POPO扮家長），乘客用特別既驗證方法確保係真仔女，一黎可以交俾個system更有效分配資源，二黎可以俾一眾admin更專注做其他duties（報導實時交通情況）。聽講寫一個要即時communication既apps都係三四十萬蚊，會唔會有IT人識寫個app出泥？成本可以眾籌或者搵黃色商家贊助。推到有心IT人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8391f704465ff1cabe84d73238b4213b03f3abf4","tid":1689122,"uid":50347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:41:24.000Z","msg":"會唔會三四十萬咁平啊"},{"pid":"87a7210d04eba8270e95fb070aee2c574195b8ec","tid":1689122,"uid":200019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:41:31.000Z","msg":"有可能驗證嗎？"}]}